short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e: Automatically uncheck the 'Stay signed in' checkbox on the Google Accounts page.
short.de: Automatisch deaktivieren Sie das Kontrollkästchen auf der Seite von Google-Konten 'Angemeldet bleiben'.
short.es: Automáticamente desmarque la "No cerrar sesión" casilla de verificación en la página de cuentas de Google
short.fr: Automatiquement décochez la "Rester connecté" case sur la page Comptes Google
short.zh_CN: 自动将取消选中该复选框的谷歌帐户页面'留在签署'。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
Stay Signed Out automatically unchecks the "Stay signed in" checkbox on the Google Accounts Sign in page.

Now, also hides "Visit My Account" pop box on the Google homepage. Neat.

It is small, fast, and unobtrusive.
long.de,es,fr,zh_CN:
Stay Signed Out automatically unchecks the "Stay signed in" checkbox on the Google Accounts Sign in page.

It is small, fast, and unobtrusive.
